OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPartly
OL,6,Fcloudy skies and some sunny intervals
OL,7,Fthis evening. Cloud increasing from
OL,8,Fthe north overnight with showery rain
OL,9,Ftoward the end of the night. Becoming
OL,10,Fbreezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FEarly cloud and rain clearing,
OL,13,Fthen dry and bright with sunny
OL,14,Fintervals and a few coastal showers.
OL,15,FBreezy, though strong winds near
OL,16,Fcoasts. Clear skies overnight, leading
OL,17,Fto ground frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
