OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBreezy
OL,6,Fand cloudy, with outbreaks of rain
OL,7,FTuesday, followed by showers. Blustery
OL,8,Fshowers, with possible thunder, and
OL,9,Fsome sunny intervals Wednesday and
OL,10,FThursday. Cool.
